body_html:
This seems like a bug, as evidenced by curl -H 'Accept-Language: ru' https://www.tensorflow.org.
It's now been brought to the attention of the right people internally in b/70993883. We can hopefully have this fixed sometime soon but I'm going to close this issue out just to get it out of triage queue. Thank you for bringing this to our attention.

This seems like a bug, as evidenced by `curl -H 'Accept-Language: ru' https://www.tensorflow.org`.
